casebody.data:
Daniel ZBYTNIUK, Employee-Plaintiff
v.
ABF FREIGHT SYSTEMS, INC. (f/k/a Cardinal Freight Carriers), Self-Insured, Employer-Defendant. No. 162P05-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 3, 2005. Neil P. Andrews, Charlotte, for ABF Freight Systems, Inc. Phillip J. Anthony, Kathrine E. Downing, Raleigh, for Daniel Zbytniuk.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 7th day of October 2005 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of November 2005."
